OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1774137775
OL,3,CDying man pleads with Lords as poll
OL,4,Cshows public back assisted deaths
OL,6,FPolling conducted for ITV News by
OL,7,FIpsos of more than a thousand UK
OL,8,Fadults found 65% of respondents either
OL,9,Fstrongly support or tend to support
OL,10,Fthe assisted dying bill following more
OL,11,Fthan a year of debate in Westminster.
OL,13,FIn contrast, 14% of respondents said
OL,14,Fthat they either strongly oppose or
OL,15,Ftend to oppose it.
OL,17,F15% said they neither support nor
OL,18,Foppose the bill, and a further 6% said
OL,19,Fthat they didn't know or didn't wish
OL,20,Fto answer.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1774137775
OL,3,CDying man pleads with Lords as poll
OL,4,Cshows public back assisted deaths
OL,6,FThe bill would allow terminally ill
OL,7,Fpeople like John to be helped to die
OL,8,Fif they had less than six months left
OL,9,Fto live.
OL,11,FBut the legislation is currently held
OL,12,Fup in the House of Lords, where peers
OL,13,Fare considering more than 1200
OL,14,Famendments.
OL,16,FITV News is featuring personal stories
OL,17,Ffrom both sides of the debate as the
OL,18,Fbill looks increasingly likely to run
OL,19,Fout of time to pass before the end of
OL,20,Fthe parliamentary session in May.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1774137775
OL,3,CDying man pleads with Lords as poll
OL,4,Cshows public back assisted deaths
OL,6,FThis week MSPs rejected a similar bill
OL,7,Fat Holyrood by 69 votes to 57. ITV
OL,8,FNews' polling includes respondents
OL,9,Ffrom Scotland.
OL,11,FJohn and his wife Liz say that the
OL,12,Ffamily has received exceptional care
OL,13,Ffrom Myton Hospice, where they have
OL,14,Fbeen able to stay together in a
OL,15,Fprivate room as John is made as
OL,16,Fcomfortable as possible.
OL,18,FIf you have a story you'd like to
OL,19,Fshare with ITV News, please contact
OL,20,Fliz.little@itn.co.uk
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1774137775
OL,3,CDying man pleads with Lords as poll
OL,4,Cshows public back assisted deaths
OL,6,FBut despite every effort, they feel
OL,7,Fthat palliative care has been unable
OL,8,Fto remove all of John's suffering and
OL,9,Fthat the choice of an assisted death
OL,10,Fwould have brought him great comfort.
OL,12,F"If those people (in the House of
OL,13,FLords) could just sit with us for a
OL,14,Fday or two and see what life is like,
OL,15,FI would hope they would have some
OL,16,Fempathy and just understand it's about
OL,17,Fgiving people choice over their own
OL,18,Fbodies," Liz says.
OL,26,@tD@AOUtD@RpmuD@FpnzD@HO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1774137775
OL,3,CDying man pleads with Lords as poll
OL,4,Cshows public back assisted deaths
OL,6,FEven John's nine-year-old daughter
OL,7,FRose has begun to notice the impact of
OL,8,FJohn's condition on his quality of
OL,9,Flife.
OL,11,F"I miss when he was very strong... He
OL,12,Falways lifted me up," she tells me.
OL,14,FNo child wants to lose their father,
OL,15,Fbut I ask Rose how she feels about her
OL,16,Fdad's illness.
OL,26,@sD@AOUtD@UO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30910
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1774137775
OL,3,CDying man pleads with Lords as poll
OL,4,Cshows public back assisted deaths
OL,6,F"I feel a bit like I want him to die
OL,7,Fquicker," she says, clearly burdened
OL,8,Fby the enormity of the thought.
OL,9,F"Because then he doesn't have to spend
OL,10,Fa long time just sitting in a bed."
OL,12,F"You want him to feel that he's at
OL,13,Fpeace?" I clarify.
OL,15,F"Yes," she replies, as her eyes look
OL,16,Finto the distance. It is a lot for
OL,17,Fsuch a young mind to contemplate.
OL,19,FI ask John if he has a message for
OL,20,Fpeers in the House of Lords as the
OL,21,FAssisted Dying Bill runs out of time.
OL,26,@nD@AOUoD@IO]qD@AOUrD@cO]tD@AOUuD@GO]wD@
OL,26,AAOUwD@FO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30911
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1774137775
OL,3,CDying man pleads with Lords as poll
OL,4,Cshows public back assisted deaths
OL,6,F"I guess it's mainly just to give
OL,7,Fpeople a choice to have the option, to
OL,8,Fgo through with it, and end things on
OL,9,Ftheir terms. Rather than just having
OL,10,Fno option but to suffer."
OL,12,F"If he wanted to keep going forever,
OL,13,FI'd support him," Liz adds.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@YO]tD@AOUuD@QO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30912
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1774137775
OL,3,CDying man pleads with Lords as poll
OL,4,Cshows public back assisted deaths
OL,6,F"But if it got too much, I'd support
OL,7,Fhim in that as well. It's devastating
OL,8,Ffor all of us, the thought that he
OL,9,Fwon't be here. But we try and do our
OL,10,Fbest because that's what he would want
OL,11,Ffor us. And we know we've got this a
OL,12,Flove that will carry on no matter
OL,13,Fwhere he is."
OL,15,FJohn died in the early hours of Friday
OL,16,Fmorning. He was 43.
OL,18,FHis family has asked us to tell his
OL,19,Fstory in his memory.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@MO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30913
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1774137775
OL,3,CDying man pleads with Lords as poll
OL,4,Cshows public back assisted deaths
OL,6,FFollowing his death, his wife Liz
OL,7,Fsaid: "Having now seen the 'full
OL,8,Fpicture,' I would have given
OL,9,Feverything for John to have been given
OL,10,Fthe option to die on his terms. It
OL,11,Fwould have helped us all to be more at
OL,12,Fpeace with the situation.
OL,14,F"It seems that for most young people
OL,15,Fdying of cancer, even a 'good death'
OL,16,Fthrough palliative care cannot take
OL,17,Faway the loss of dignity and prolonged
OL,18,Fsuffering. And I now have the trauma
OL,19,Fof these memories to add to the grief
OL,20,Fwhich is particularly hard."
OL,26,@oD@GOUvD@AOU|D@\O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30914
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1774137775
OL,3,CDying man pleads with Lords as poll
OL,4,Cshows public back assisted deaths
OL,6,FOn Friday, ITV News will feature the
OL,7,Fstory of a mother with a terminal
OL,8,Fillness who opposes assisted dying.
OL,10,FPolling by Ipsos was based on the
OL,11,FAssisted Dying Bill as originally
OL,12,Fintroduced to Parliament. Amendments
OL,13,Fhave subsequently been made to the
OL,14,FBill including replacing the sign-off
OL,15,Fof a High Court judge with a three-
OL,16,Fperson panel, made up of a social
OL,17,Fworker, psychiatrist and senior legal
OL,18,Ffigure.
OL,20,FIpsos have published further
OL,21,Fexplanation here.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30915
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1774137775
OL,3,CDying man pleads with Lords as poll
OL,4,Cshows public back assisted deaths
OL,6,FFor ITV News, Ipsos interviewed a
OL,7,Frepresentative quota sample of 1,116
OL,8,Fadults aged 18-75 in the United
OL,9,FKingdom using its online i:omnibus
OL,10,Fbetween March 2026 13 to 17 . The
OL,11,Fsample obtained is representative of
OL,12,Fthe population with quotas on age,
OL,13,Fgender, region and working status. The
OL,14,Fdata was weighted to the known offline
OL,15,Fpopulation proportions for age,
OL,16,Fworking status and social grade within
OL,17,Fgender, and for government office
OL,18,Fregion and education, to reflect the
OL,19,Fadult population of the United Kingdom.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
